Prevention of Undesirable Isomerization during Olefin Metathesis<br>
S. H. Hong, D. P. Sander, C. W. Lee, R. H. Grubbs, <i>J. Am. Chem. Soc.</i>, <b>2005</b>, <i>127</i>, 17160-17161.</p>
<p><a href="../abstracts/lit2/017.shtm"><img src="../abstracts/lit2/017a.gif"></a><br>
A Rapid and Simple Cleanup Procedure for Metathesis Reactions<br>
