135</i>, 1276-1279.</p>
<p><a href="../abstracts/lit1/474.shtm"><img src="../abstracts/lit1/474b.gif"></a><br>
Advanced Fine-Tuning of Grubbs/Hoveyda Olefin Metathesis Catalysts: A 
Further Step toward an Optimum Balance between Antinomic Properties<br>
